values:
This is a locked journal. It contains private pictures, thoughts, feelings and so forth of myself, my family and my friends. My gorgeous sister is featured in my default userpic and I'd LOVE for you to not steal it (although let's face it, some of you people f'n suck). 

If you wish to be added to this journal, leave me a comment and I'll get back to you as soon as possible. 

Do not add me first.

Edit: I've removed all friends, if you want to be re-added, just let me know!
